{"tid":709750,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係新西蘭","createTime":"2018-06-20T09:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T23:37:46.000Z","uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f9a448501f65da6fb38350284d8656dcf770f592","tid":709750,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:08:49.000Z","msg":"過幾日落 Queenstown 有乜野必做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b84611bd6b3934b6f6270b1d0b69bd3b9f47cec","tid":709750,"uid":693,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:09:19.000Z","msg":"紐西蘭呀"},{"pid":"83a65a9479a78cbb592f1c1c718e38fed353eda9","tid":709750,"uid":126027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T21:33:31.000Z","msg":"skydiving bungyjump <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5a5f53d0018cd6b740c70234371074dbf13516","tid":709750,"uid":25657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T21:50:44.000Z","msg":"新？邊度新呀睇過 <br />\n紐西蘭呀！！！"},{"pid":"08d294ba1cc9e1b8e0e7dd6100377d0dd3902fbf","tid":709750,"uid":31181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"83a65a9479a78cbb592f1c1c718e38fed353eda9","tid":709750,"uid":126027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T21:33:31.000Z","msg":"skydiving bungyjump <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T05:25:26.000Z","msg":"我準備好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11901d68368ea9f5d0e5ef933b8f9746fdc2dafc","tid":709750,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T07:05:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180621/58344438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180621%2F58344438&d=f1ak%2FKx76gFv0bJ44sDKYG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=cba1f02e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180621%2F58344438&h=4ab5a4c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180621/58344438</a><br />\n<br />\n「這已不是會否發生的問題，是何時發生。」新西蘭專家指，當地有巨型火山即將在未來爆發，還屬500年一遇的大規模火山爆發，可嚴重破壞整個北島。<br />\n<br />\n位於新西蘭北島西岸埃格蒙特國家公園（Egmont National Park）的塔拉納基火山（Mount Taranaki）每500年會發生一次中度至嚴重的爆發，對上一次的爆發是在1655年。<br />\n專家預計未來50年內將會有一次火山爆發，威力可摧毀北島。當地的5年民防計劃報告警告，未來各年火山爆發的機會率倍增，由本來的1.6%升至3.1%。<br />\n現時塔拉納基火山登上2500米峰的行山路線每年吸引約45萬名行山客，火山爆發危機不單影響遊客，還有附近城鎮和建築物。一旦爆發，火山會釋放大量火山灰和碎屑，引發熔岩流、火山泥流、洪水泛濫等等。<br />\n不過目前還未有跡象顯示火山爆發，當局有信心其警報機制會在適當的時機發出通報。"},{"pid":"9a6a05ea139a98729d814a6b792855fa1c526051","tid":709750,"uid":54095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T07:07:19.000Z","msg":"新你老母 紐西蘭唔撚識？"},{"pid":"82d5fe74ff7f6258a8dd5a5b18fe1677bc1112f6","tid":709750,"uid":32694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T21:25:19.000Z","msg":"滑雪 行雪山 玩jetboat 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實個度好多local tour 可以join 不過都幾貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2df1303dd96aaf151cc42f378e7166d5a3578e","tid":709750,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T23:30:40.000Z","msg":"樓豬選擇性失明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696810e9a0ad3432f86ceaee817cb3af3fafdb2a","tid":709750,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T23:37:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}